These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, cabbage, carrot, lettuce
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, mystery, romance, scientific
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, prince, siglo, fonseca
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hamster, horse, rat
 1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
 2. the person eating banana is in an even position##4
 3. the blend-smoker is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
 4. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
 7. the prince-smoker is the person eating carrot##1
 8. the owner of the horse is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the rat and the person watching scientific movies##2
10. the person eating banana is the owner of the rat##1
11. the person watching romance movies is the person eating lettuce##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | carrot  | banana    | lettuce    | cabbage   |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery     | time-travel   | romance       | scientific    |
| Cigar   | prince | blend | fonseca    | siglo |
| Pet           | hamster | rat       | chinchilla | horse     |

