.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, eggplant, kale, peas
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, collecting, drawing, woodworking
House: townhouse, tower, craftsman, cape-cod
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, funk, rock, ambient
 1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an even position##4
 2. the tower house is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person eating kale##1
 4. the person eating eggplant is the townhouse house##1
 5. the fan of ambient is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
 6. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
 7. the person eating peas is on the right of the person eating kale##1
 8. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
 9. the craftsman house is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating kale is in an odd position##4
11. the craftsman house is the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Food          | carrot  | eggplant    | kale     | peas       |
| Hobby         | drawing | woodworking | baking   | collecting |
| House   | craftsman | townhouse   | tower   | cape-cod    |
| Music-Genre         | rock | ambient  | country | funk   |

