.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, fonseca, chaman, vegafina
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, july, march, august
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, chess, sudoku, woodworking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, parkour, surfing
 1. the dunhill-smoker is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
 4. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4
 5. the fonseca-smoker is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
 7. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is the person who's hobby is chess##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
11. the chaman-smoker is the person who's birthday is in august##1
12. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Cigar   | vegafina       | chaman   | dunhill   | fonseca   |
| Birthday       | july        | august | december    | march       |
| Hobby      | woodworking | chess    | sudoku  | card-games |
| Sport      | ice-hockey  | parkour  | cycling | surfing    |

