.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: british, italian, russian, polish
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, magic-tricks, rock-climbing, sudoku
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, librarian, manager, musician
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, apricot, red, yellow
 1. the person who likes apricot is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person who likes light-blue and the polish##2
 3. the manager is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
 4. the librarian is the british##1
 5. the bartender is on the left or right of the librarian##3
 6. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
 7. the italian is the bartender##1
 8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the librarian##1
 9. the british is on the left or right of the person who likes yellow##3
10. the librarian is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
11. the person who likes yellow is on the left or right of the russian##3
12. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who likes red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Nationality    | russian    | polish      | british          | italian    |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | sudoku       | rock-climbing | gardening |
| Job     | musician     | manager      | librarian     | bartender |
| Color   | apricot   | yellow | red        | light-blue   |

