The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, balloon-flower, azalea, sunflower
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, folk, gospel
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, german, indian
 1. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the librarian##1
 2. the librarian is on the left or right of the designer##3
 3. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 4. the entrepreneur is on the left or right of the designer##3
 5. the librarian is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan of gospel is between the german and the fan of dubstep##2
 7. the fan of folk is the person who growsazalea##1
 8. the designer is the person who growsazalea##1
 9. the colombian is on the far right##1
10. the canadian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Job      | entrepreneur  | designer    | librarian       | analyst       |
| Flower          | sunflower    | azalea | balloon-flower | tulip     |
| Music-Genre   | classical | folk        | gospel    | dubstep   |
| Nationality   | canadian  | german      | indian    | colombian |

