.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-7::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, surfing, lacrosse, badminton
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, hot-chocolate, sprite, iced-tea
4 different pets are kept: ferret, frog, goat, lizard
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, skateboard, subway, trike
 1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 3. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 4. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 7. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 8. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
 9. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
11. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
12. the owner of the ferret is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4      |
| Sport   | surfing | lacrosse    | badminton  | cricket      |
| Beverage   | tea      | sprite | iced-tea | hot-chocolate   |
| Pet           | goat       | lizard | ferret   | frog       |
| Transport     | trike      | subway | scooter  | skateboard |

