4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, dannemann, fonseca, prince
 1. the prince-smoker is in an odd position##4
 2. the bolivar-smoker is between the prince-smoker and the fonseca-smoker##2
 3. the american is on the left of the victorian house##1
 4. the person watching sports movies is in an odd position##4
 5. the spanish is on the right of the nigerian##1
 6. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the cottage house##3
 7. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the victorian house##1
 8. the cottage house is on the left of the australian##1
 9. the bolivar-smoker is between the american and the person watching fantasy movies##2
10. the cottage house is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
11. the ranch-style house is in an even position##4
12. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3

.:: Answer ::.
