The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, skiing, snowboarding, water-polo
 1. the person eating mango is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person driving the helicopter and the person who's sport is skiing##2
 4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 5. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
 6. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person eating potato##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in october is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person driving the helicopter##1
 9. the person eating garlic is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
11. the person eating garlic is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person eating potato##1
13. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |      4       |
