.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lilypy, azalea, lily, daffodil
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, french, indonesian, polish
4 different pets are kept: ferret, snake, cat, horse
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, helicopter, skateboard
 1. the person who growsdaffodil is the owner of the cat##1
 2. the owner of the cat is between the australian and the polish##2
 3. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
 4. the person driving the car is on the left of the french##1
 5. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 6. the person who growsazalea is the owner of the snake##1
 7. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
 8. the polish is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
10. the australian is in an even position##4
11. the australian is on the far right##1
12. the person who growslilypy is on the right of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Flower   | azalea      | lilypy | daffodil     | lily        |
| Nationality   | indonesian | polish  | french     | australian |
| Pet         | snake    | ferret | cat      | horse |
| Transport     | skateboard | car     | helicopter | bike       |

 